General.Name: Bigtincan Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Bigtincan Holdings Limited operates as a sales enablement automation company. The company's platforms include Bigtincan Learning Hub, a learning platform that reinforce sales plays and product knowledge with quizzes, curated content, and self-guided microlearning lessons.; and Bigtincan Engagement Hub, a platform solution, which combines content, communication, and interaction insights. It also offers integration solutions; security solutions for the secure distribution and management of documents and other media content. The company's solutions are used for sales, marketing, and filed service. It serves life sciences, financial, retail, technology, manufacturing, telecommunication, and energy industries, as well as governments. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Sydney, Australia.
